Gabriel Stevenson, onye a maara dị ka Like, bụ ónyé America na-emepụta ihe ndekọ, ónyé na-eti egwu, DJ na onye na-ede egwu
Onye a họpụtara na Grammy ugboro atọ, ọ malitere ịrụ ọrụ na Pacific Division, otu hip hop atọ, nke a maara nke ọma dị ka Pac Div na 2006.
N'afọ 2012, o mepụtara Kendrick Lamar's "Sing About Me" na Good Kid, M.A.A.D City
Ọ natara nhọpụta Grammy Award abụọ na 56th Grammy Awards: Album of the Year na Best Rap Album

N'afọ 2016, o mepụtara Anderson"Room in Here" nke Paak gosipụtara The Game na Sonyae Elise na album Malibu. Abọm ahụ nwetara nhọpụta Grammy màkà Best Urban Contemporary Album na 59th Annual Grammy Awards
Like nwèrè mmepụta ihe na ndị na-ese ihe dịka Mac Miller, Ab-Soul, Joey Badass, Nick Grant, Asher Roth, Ill Camille na Currensy.
Like ewepụtala égwu dị ka ónyé na-ese égwu n'onwe ya
O weputara abọm instrumental, Zesty na Lightwork na 2014 na Emeralds na 2016
Na Septemba 30, 2016, ọ wepụtara abọm rap mbụ ya, Songs Made While High, nke gosipụtara Anderson.Paak, Buddy, na Kali Uchis.
N'afọ 2017, Pac Div jikọtara ọnụ mà hazie ka ha wepụta abọm na ngwụcha afọ.
